main event: Multiple sightings of unidentified flying objects were reported over Bunkie, Louisiana between August 31 and September 7, 1965.
interesting points: Witnesses reported seeing multiple circular and glowing objects hovering with various colors such as red and blue,The objects were described as having no sound and were observed to move rapidly, sometimes changing direction abruptly,At least 10 individual reports were received from the local residents of Bunkie, Louisiana, including a local police officer and several others observed the objects,Reports indicated the observation of physical evidence in forms of ground burns and impressions in some cases, The sightings coincided with a period when the Air Force recorded a high volume of similar unidentified aerial phenomena reports across the Midwest.
sighted object: multiple circular and glowing unidentified flying objects
witness description: Local residents, including police officers, and trained military personnel.
